OL,5,G0000 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,6,     FA devastating car crash leads to a
OL,7,     Fmanhunt for the driver and two
OL,8,     Fpassengers, at least one of whom
OL,9,     Fis bleeding heavily, and a
OL,10,     F13-year-old cyclist suffers a
OL,11,     Ftraumatic femur fracture.
OL,12,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FThe doctors of Hall Green Health
OL,14,     Fcome face to face with some rare
OL,15,     Fconditions. It's a reminder that
OL,16,     Fwhen you're a GP, you never know
OL,17,     Fwhat is going to walk through your
OL,18,     Fdoor.
