OL,5,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,7,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,8,     Funder the microscope. John checks
OL,9,     Fover a man who fell six feet on to
OL,10,     Fconcrete and may have complex
OL,11,     Ffractures.
OL,12,G0245 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Emma McMullen has her work cut
OL,14,     Fout trying to help a patient with
OL,15,     Fa challenging condition - and ends
OL,16,     Fup needing a wipe down! And a
OL,17,     Fpatient's mole makes it hard to
OL,18,     Fbrush her hair.
